<% provide(:title, 'Organizations') %>

<h1>Organizations</h1>

<% if !logged_in? %> 
  <div align="right"> 
    <%= link_to "Organizational Log in", login_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %>
  </div>
<% end %> 

<ul>
  <% @users.each do | org | %>
  <li><%= org.name %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>
  This is a dynamic page of all the organizations that have signed up to be part
  of this website.  Click the above Log In button to sign up as an
  organization.  Once you have signed up, your information will be saved and
  the name of you organization will appear on this page!
</p>
<p>
  Eventually, each organization profile will have their own user photo, a short
  description of who they are and a way to contact them.  Each volunteering opportunity
  will be linked to an organization on this list.
</p>
